<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/110620656-wit">Wit</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I’m not even sure if this is a real question, but I’ll answer it anyway. Considering that it’s called Einstein’s Dreams I don’t think Einstein went th<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I’m not even sure if this is a real question, but I’ll answer it anyway. Considering that it’s called Einstein’s Dreams I don’t think Einstein went there. The premise of the book is that this is what Einstein was dreaming about as he theorized on the nature of time. Whether or not they’re real is irrelevant where fantasy is concerned.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
